{
  "title": "Fizzik",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "About",
      "lines": [
        "Polyphonic physical-modeling synth.",
        "A strike (exciter) rings TWO coupled",
        "resonators per voice: String, Beam,",
        "Plate or Membrane. Couple cross-feeds",
        "them for emergent, living timbres.",
        "6 voices. Press pads for aftertouch."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Patch (root)",
      "lines": [
        "Preset: 30 sounds, click-free switch.",
        "Rnd Patch: new random instrument.",
        "Rnd Exc: new strike (hear next note).",
        "Rnd Reson: new resonator pair.",
        "Rnd All: randomize EVERYTHING (FX,",
        "LFOs, aftertouch too; limiter safe).",
        "Cutoff/Resonance/Type: global filter.",
        "Menu: Voicing (12 analog filters)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Exciter",
      "lines": [
        "The strike. Shapes the NEXT note.",
        "Exc Mix: noise burst vs mallet tick.",
        "Crackle: random impulse clicks.",
        "Color(+Reso): strike filter, dark",
        "thud to bright snap.",
        "Attack/Decay: burst shape, 0.2-400ms.",
        "Long decay = bowed/scraped textures.",
        "Vel Level/Color: velocity response."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Reson A / B",
      "lines": [
        "Model: String (waveguide), Beam",
        "(kalimba), Plate (bell), Membrane",
        "(drum).",
        "Structure: stiffness/morph/aspect.",
        "Decay: ring time. Damp: HF decay",
        "(modal brightness lives here).",
        "Position: strike point (comb tone).",
        "Tone: string brightness. Tune: +-24.",
        "Tension: hard hits bend pitch up",
        "(String/Beam only)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Voice",
      "lines": [
        "Couple: A<->B cross-feedback. THE",
        "knob — from clean to interacting,",
        "self-limiting, never blows up.",
        "Balance: A vs B mix. Glide: porta.",
        "Amp Atk/Rel: amplitude envelope.",
        "Spread: per-note stereo. Drive:",
        "warm saturation. Level: patch gain."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "FX / FX 2",
      "lines": [
        "FX: Reverb (mix/size/damp), stereo",
        "ping-pong Delay (time warps like",
        "tape), Width (M/S stereo).",
        "FX2: Tone/Body EQ, Chorus, Glue",
        "compressor, and the output limiter:",
        "Lim Drive pushes loudness, Lim Ceil",
        "is a brickwall. Default ceiling is",
        "low for headphone safety - raise it",
        "for more level."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Mod",
      "lines": [
        "Two LFOs: Rate 0.05-20Hz, Depth,",
        "Shape (Sine/Tri/Saw/Square/S&H),",
        "Target: Cutoff, Pitch, Couple,",
        "Balance, Tension, Tone, Reso.",
        "Try slow sine to Couple: breathing",
        "interaction. S&H to Pitch: broken",
        "machine."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Aftertouch",
      "lines": [
        "Press held pads - each note responds",
        "to its own finger (poly AT).",
        "AT Preset: 10 feels (Bow, Cello,",
        "Swell, Wild...). Bright: opens tone.",
        "Bow: pressure re-excites the note -",
        "plucks bloom into bowed sustains.",
        "Cutoff: opens global filter.",
        "Vib/Bend(+Rate): pressure vibrato",
        "and pitch. Curve: soft or hard",
        "pressure response."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Tips",
      "lines": [
        "Detune B +7 or +12 from A, raise",
        "Couple: instant complexity.",
        "AT Bow + long Amp Rel = bowing.",
        "Ladder voicings self-oscillate at",
        "max Resonance (bounded, safe).",
        "Presets keep your filter/AT/FX2",
        "setup - it is a global layer.",
        "Rnd All never touches Lim Ceil."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
